SummaryEnglish: Nagisa Misumi and Honoka Yukishiro couldn't be more different. Nagisa is sporty and Honoka bookish, and while they attend the same school, they have very little in common - until one day, a shower of shooting stars brings two very unlikely visitors into their lives: Mippuru and Meppuru, refugees from the Garden of Light, which has been conquered by Darkness. Endowed with new and startling powers, Nagisa and Honoka become Cure Black and Cure White, magical defenders of the light - together, they are Futari Wa Pretty Cure.
Aliases: ふたりはプリキュア Max Heart

1.TitleEnglish: Pretty Cure Max Heart: The Movie
1.SummaryEnglish: The Courageous Warriors of the Garden of Hope have summoned Nagisa, Honoka, and Hikari to protect their kingdom from a witch who plans to steal the Diamond Line, which is a set of jewelry the queen of the Garden of Hope wears to a ceremony every year to replenish the water of the kingdom. The witch plans to resurrect the Dark Lord and if she does so, not only will the Garden of Hope be destroyed, but other kingdoms in the galaxies, including the Garden of Rainbows and the Garden of Light.

2.TitleEnglish: Pretty Cure Max Heart: Friends of the Snow-Laden Sky
2.SummaryEnglish: On his way to visit the Queen of the Garden of Light, the Sage of the Garden of Clouds accidentally drops the egg of the Houhou. The egg lands in the Garden of Rainbows, where it is found by Hikari, attracting the attention of a powerful pair of servants of the Dark Lord.

1.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa Misumi and Honoka Yukishiro couldn't be more different. Nagisa is sporty and Honoka bookish, and while they attend the same school, they have very little in common - until one day, a shower of shooting stars brings two very unlikely visitors into their lives: Mippuru and Meppuru, refugees from the Garden of Light, which has been conquered by Darkness. Endowed with new and startling powers, Nagisa and Honoka become Cure Black and Cure White, magical defenders of the light - together, they are Futari Wa Pretty Cure.
Nagisa Misumi and Honoka Yukishiro, two classmates who've never spoken to one another are called to be Pretty Cure by two unexpected visitors.

2.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka must figure out what's behind a citywide power outage, while relying on Mipple and Mepple to guide them in the dark.

3.SummaryEnglish: Pisard poses as a student teacher in an attempt to get the Prism Stones from Nagisa. He becomes Mr. Komodo and hypnotizes the girls teacher into to bring the girls to the gym where they fight with the gym equipment. Pisard also uses the still hypnotized teacher as both a threat and a distraction and gets the girls off their guard. The girls and their teacher get wrapped in the curtains in the gym and are tossed around until their teacher loses consciousness which ticks the girls off. They use marble twister and send Pisard back and save their teacher. After awhile their teacher wakes up to see the girls out of class and gives them detention with the girls concluding that she forgot everything.

4.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka are put in charge of a trip to the art museum, which is targeted by Pisard.

5.SummaryEnglish: Pisard's final episode. He desperately tries to win against Pretty Cure, knowing it's his last chance.

6.SummaryEnglish: Mepple has accidentally lost the Prism Hopish. The girls go hiking to look for it and are attacked by Gekidrago. .

7.SummaryEnglish: When the Dark Zone attacks during a lacrosse tournament, Nagisa must choose between helping Honoka or her team.

8.SummaryEnglish: Honoka's well-meaning attempt at matchmaking between Nagisa and Fuji-P backfires, causing a rift in Pretty Cure.

9.SummaryEnglish: Mepple has fallen ill. Just when Nagisa realizes this, the vice-principal confiscates him. Nagisa has to retrieve him and cure his illness before it's too late.

10.SummaryEnglish: Honoka's parents come home for her birthday. However, a series of events lead to Honoka and her parents being held hostage in a jewelry store as Gekidrago strikes.

11.SummaryEnglish: Gekidrago's final episode. A trip to the aquarium for Ryouta's school project leads to Nagisa and Honoka having to defend him from the enemy.

12.SummaryEnglish: The new enemy, Poisonny appears, playing on Nagisa and Honoka's weaknesses to steal Mepple and Mipple.

13.SummaryEnglish: A new student, Kiriya, secretly Poisonny's younger brother, transfers to Nagisa and Honoka's school.

14.SummaryEnglish: Two girls are impersonating Pretty Cure. Poisonny hopes to force the girls to exchange the Prism Stones for the impostors.

15.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka happen to be at the same vacation spot. They take advantage of this and go on an island adventure.

16.SummaryEnglish: Poisonny's Zakenna possess the body of the school superstar, creating an army of copies of her all over the school.

17.SummaryEnglish: Honoka invites Nagisa to bring in the harvest on a friend's farm where she'll be working alongside Fujipi.

18.SummaryEnglish: Poisonny traps Nagisa and Honoka in a mirror maze during their midterm exams.

19.SummaryEnglish: Ilkuubo shows up and surprises the girls with the power of the Dotsukuzon.

20.SummaryEnglish: Poisonny's final episode. Poisonny impersonates Honoka and tries to trick Nagisa into giving her Mepple.

21.SummaryEnglish: Kiriya confesses to Honoka about being part of the Dotsukuzon and willingly gives her his Prism Stone. Kiriya then goes back to Dotsukuzon to face his punishment.

22.SummaryEnglish: Chuutaro finds an abandoned puppy. Nagisa and Honoka try to find its owner but run into Ilkuubo, who finds out where the Stones are hidden, on the way.

23.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka's training camps experience weird event from power outages to dying trees. They find out that Ilkuubo is behind it as he forces the Prism Hopish out of hiding and takes it.

24.TitleEnglish: Match Point! Pretty Cure Vs. Ilkubo
24.SummaryEnglish: Ilkuubbo finally takes the last two Stones but doesn't know how powerful they really are.

25.TitleEnglish: Return to the Garden of Light
25.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka travel to the Field of Light to bring about the Power of Creation.

26.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka are kidnapped to the Dotsukuzon where they try to defeat Jyaku-King.

27.SummaryEnglish: Pollun gets lost after going to back to the Field of Rainbows with Mipple and Mepple.

28.SummaryEnglish: It is an extremely hot day and Nagisa and Honoka meet a new enemy.

29.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka go to a Summer festival and meet their third enemy.

30.SummaryEnglish: Pollun sneaks to school and gets the girls in trouble. When the guardian is lured out of his hiding place, he gives Pollun the power of the prism stones.

31.SummaryEnglish: Porun, curious about the Garden of Rainbows (Earth), decides to take a visit.

32.SummaryEnglish: Porun is feeling homesick, so Nagisa and Honoka take him to the amusement park.

33.SummaryEnglish: Shiho feeling down after she misses a shot at lacrosse practice and decides to quit the team.

34.SummaryEnglish: It's Track day and Field Day at Verone Junior High and Nagisa's set to race against Yuka.

35.SummaryEnglish: Kazuki, the star player of the basketball team, asks Nagisa to go chestnut picking on her birthday with him and she has a hard time turning him down.

36.SummaryEnglish: The Guardian's been imprisoned by the Dark Zone, but a careless mistake by the Zakennas allows him to escape.

37.SummaryEnglish: The Cherry Blossom class are planning to play Romeo and Juliet, and Nagisa and Honoka are chosen to play the main roles respectively.

38.SummaryEnglish: t's the weekend and the girls are excited for their day of shopping, but plans are derailed when Nagisa's dad. Fortunately, Ryouta steps in and delivers his dad's documents by himself.

39.SummaryEnglish: Miss Yoshimi has announced that she's getting married and the class has decided to present her with a wedding gift.

40.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa goes to a sleepover at Honoka's house and they both encounter Beruzei in their dreams and must fight him.

41.SummaryEnglish: It's the Lacrosse Championship Finals and Verone Junior High is set to play Otag Junior High.

42.SummaryEnglish: The Dark Zone figure out a way to separate Pretty Cure and it's up to Nagisa to find Honoka before she is consumed by the darkness!

43.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa has a friend named Yui, who has a crush on Fujipi... what happens next?

44.SummaryEnglish: Winter vacation is around the corner and Verone holds a Christmas Dance.

45.SummaryEnglish: The Eighth Grade Ensemble has won the choir challenge to represent Verone Junior High at the district championships. Chiaki makes a last minute decision to change the song they’re going to sing and the girls persuade the rest of the class that it’s the right move.

46.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka are excited for the new year, but before they can even enjoy their first day at school, the Dark Zone attacks. They’ve figured out that Porun has the power of the Prism Stones inside him so they’ve come to get him.

47.SummaryEnglish: After losing both the Guardian and the Prism Stones, Nagisa and Honoka have to follow Juna, Regine and Belzei back to the Dark Zone.

48.SummaryEnglish: The Dark King’s not very happy with his dark warriors. They’ve stolen what he feels is rightfully his and now Pretty Cure has to stand back and watch as the dark enemies battle it out.

49.SummaryEnglish: It’s the final showdown. Either Pretty Cure defeats the Dark King or the darkness will consume the universe.

2.TitleEnglish: Futari wa Pretty Cure Max Heart
2.SummaryEnglish: In Max Heart, Nagisa and Honoka meet the mysterious Hikari Kujou, who is soon revealed to be the "Life" of the Queen, whose powers were scattered into the form of twelve "Heartiels" following her battle with the Dark King. Meanwhile, remnants of the Dark Zone are protecting a mysterious boy, who is suspected of being the "Life" of the Dark King. Joined by Hikari, who gains the power to become Shiny Luminous, the Pretty Cures once again fight against the Dark Zone in order to retrieve the Heartiels and restore the Queen.

1.TitleEnglish: We are still Pretty Cure! The legend continues through thick and thin!
1.SummaryEnglish: After the Queen was dangerously wounded from the fight with Evil King, she separates into the parts that make her. It is now up to Nagisa and Honoka to become Cure Black and White again after Mepple and Mipple awaken once more as someone attempts to resurrect the Evil King.

2.TitleEnglish: The freshman is a profound mystery! But she is really full of riddles
2.SummaryEnglish: The girls try to learn more about the mysterious Hikari while searching for the missing Heartiels.

3.TitleEnglish: Could this be destiny? Porun and Hikari's approaching encounter
3.SummaryEnglish: After Pollun runs off to locate Seekun, he and Hikari run into one-another. When he takes off she decides to follow after him and learns something about her new friends...

4.TitleEnglish: You are not alone! A premonition that two moods overlap
4.SummaryEnglish: Hikari tries to determine just who or what Pretty Cure is as Nagisa tries to find another solution to deal with her noisy room guests without alerting anyone of their presence. In this time, Hikari and Pollun express a desire to help the Cures out.

5.TitleEnglish: A gallant appearance! My name is Shiny Luminous
5.SummaryEnglish: Cure Black and Cure White welcome their brand new teammate, Shiny Luminous and help her adjust to her newfound abilities. In this time they start wondering what Hikari's connection with the Queen is.

6.TitleEnglish: Be careful! Hikari's errand peril is a defeat
6.SummaryEnglish: Akane sends Hikari shopping with Nagisa and Honoka and Hikari gets temporally lost. She manages to get the shopping done and join up with Nagisa and Honoka again but they are attacked by Uraganos on the way back.

7.TitleEnglish: Fight, Nagisa! The prodigious power of housework at the scene of a fire
7.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa's Mom goes to her high-school reunion and leaves Nagisa to do the chores. Nagisa slacks off at first but then gets to it after a visit from Honoka.

8.TitleEnglish: Let your worries drive off! Link Hikari's ties with everyone!
8.SummaryEnglish: Nakao, Akane's colleague, tells her to close the Tako Cafe and return to her original job. She becomes worried and Hikari, Nagisa and Honoka helps her not to close the café.

9.TitleEnglish: Do not disturb! Honoka's most important day
9.SummaryEnglish: It's Honoka's birthday and her parents come to visit her after being away for their jobs. They take her to a French restaurant but the power gets cut off and Viblis attacks.

10.TitleEnglish: On the verge of panic! Don't take this dangerous field trip practice seriously!
10.SummaryEnglish: Honoka and Nagisa's class goes on a field trip to a cake factory but are attacked by Viblis.

11.TitleEnglish: Big pinch! Don't hang your heart in this one-shot turnaround
11.SummaryEnglish: It's the Lacrosse Championship and the team are set to take on another school. But a fallout with two of the members causes the team to lose, but Nagisa manages to make them work together. Meanwhile, Hikari gets an encounter with Viblis but is not able to fight her herself. Later on, Honoka and Nagisa comes to the rescue and tells Hikari not to fight the Dark Zone alone

12.TitleEnglish: Business prosperity! Welcome the Cafe's Plateau!
12.SummaryEnglish: Akane takes Nagisa, Honoka and Hikari to a festival in the highlands for their work in the takoyaki shop.

13.TitleEnglish: Nagisa's great parent-child battle? Neglecting a mother's heart?
13.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa has an argument with her mother and feels that she is annoying. But after a conversation with her father, she realises all the trouble that her mother has gone through to look after Nagisa, so she goes home to make an apology.

14.TitleEnglish: Go for it, Fuji-P-senpai! Nagisa's cheering flag of spirit
14.SummaryEnglish: Fujipi's soccer team has a match with another school and Nagisa, Honoka and Hikari go to cheer him on. But Circulas appears in the middle of the match, so they leave the game to prevent the match from being disrupted by him.

15.TitleEnglish: A senior's aspiration is a great close friend!
15.SummaryEnglish: Hikari goes out with her friends Nao and Miu. Meanwhile, Honoka studies at a library whilst Nagisa goes to a bakery to get bread for her mother. They all meet up at the same area and Nao persuades Nagisa into playing basketball with some boys.

16.TitleEnglish: Nagisa's in high spirits! The lucky color is in the pink!
16.SummaryEnglish: Shiho and Rina tell Nagisa that her horoscopes predicts a good week for her and that her lucky colour is yellow. Nagisa does not believe it, but after a series of good events, she decides to not study for her mid-term exams and instead rely on her luck. During the test, Uraganos attacks, and Nagisa, Honoka and Hikari fight him.

17.TitleEnglish: What's this? A distressed Honoka's meeting for reading research papers
17.SummaryEnglish: The Science Fair is coming up and Honoka and the Science Club do not know what theme they should do for the fair so they redo the Lightning theme that we done last year (as seen in Pretty Cure). Honoka feels that it is not the right choice but after a while, she changes the theme to "Trash and Us" and everyone works hard on it. On the day of the Science Fair, Uraganos attacked Honoka and Yukiro but Nagisa and Hikari made it on time to fight him off.

18.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa's family and Honoka go on a camping trip, and Hikari joins them later on. Chuutaro runs away, and the three girls chase after him, only to find Uraganos. They fight him off and return to Nagisa's parents, but they could not go to the waterfall because Nagisa's dad was concerned about the rain. When they visit Akane, they find out that a landslide happened by the waterfall. Intelligen gives Nagisa, Honoka and Hikari some notepads and goes inside the Chairect.

19.TitleEnglish: Hikari is worried! Nagisa's changing schools--Unbelievable!!
19.SummaryEnglish: When Nagisa overhears her father talking about moving to Osaka, she feels worried about Honoka and Hikari's reaction to the news. Fortunately, it was her father's boss who was moving, but Hikari thinks that Nagisa is moving and finds it hard to tell Honoka.

20.SummaryEnglish: After noticing how strange Rina has been the girls discover she has been taking care of a baby raccoon. As she tries to adjust to saying goodbye to it, Nagisa and Honoka are overwhelmed by their own sadness when they realize that one day they will have to part with Mepple and Mipple.

21.TitleEnglish: So soon? So often!? A forbidden encounter
21.SummaryEnglish: Hikari bonds with a boy named Daiki and tries to help him feel better after he reveals he got into a dispute with his parents. Meanwhile, the boy in the mansion is finally allowed outside of the Mansion of Darkness.

22.TitleEnglish: The horror of Baldez! Pretty Cure cornered
22.SummaryEnglish: Pretty Cure is confronted by the toughest villain yet, Baldez...

23.TitleEnglish: Rebound the dark powers! Hope uncovers a new power!
23.SummaryEnglish: The girls go to Lake Hyoutan with Seekun and Intelligen to look for the 'shining piece of Earth surrounded by six pillars'. But when Baldez figures out their plans he steps in to take it and the Power of Creation for himself.

24.TitleEnglish: Adolescent full throttle! Yuka-senpai and Nagisa's top deciding battle!
24.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa and Honoka are preparing to lead their summer camp teams, but to their surprise, Hikari decides to join. Along with Yuka - who doesn't actually seem to be there for the clubs themself

25.SummaryEnglish: The girls, along with Honoka's grandmother, decide to visit the lake one warm summer day. Seeing that Hikari has a problem, Sanae encourages her to never give up and she uses this advice when the girls get attacked by Viblis.

26.TitleEnglish: Losing Nagisa! Everyone is worried and greatly afraid!
26.SummaryEnglish: As the Summer Festival approaches, Nagisa worries over not having a plan for the future. Unknowingly, someone else she knows is in the same boat as she is and with that persons help, she may realize that she doesn't need to hurry.

27.TitleEnglish: Don't finish your homework yet! Pears and storms and Zakennah!
27.SummaryEnglish: The girls join Akane as she visits a Pear Orchard in search of a new menu item, and during this, Nagisa decides to base her research on the Pears and lends the couple who own it a hand.

28.TitleEnglish: Veroune panic! The naughty ghost-hunting princess
28.SummaryEnglish: Rumors around school about the ghost Ruriko haunting it begin to surface. At first the girls don't believe it but after a series of strange events, they start to reconsider the possibilities.

29.TitleEnglish: No way...Seriously...Really? Porun's great babysitter strategy!
29.SummaryEnglish: Lulun goes to live with Nagisa after annoying Pollun but when this arrangement doesn't work out, they return her to Hikari. In this time, the siblings learn about the bond between brother and sister.

30.TitleEnglish: Do your best, Luloon! Weave the future with the power of light
30.SummaryEnglish: The girls go for a trip to the Amusement Park and Hikari makes a vow to protect Lulun from harm. But Circulas shows up to get rid of her, angering the girls.

31.TitleEnglish: Valdez reborn! Break through with teamwork at the last second!!
31.SummaryEnglish: It's a Lacrosse tournament and Verone Academy is set to face Kakatouan school; however, things prove to be difficult when the rivaling team easily gains a lead. To make matters worse, Viblis has decided to show up.

32.TitleEnglish: Protect us from darkness! This world's most important smile!
32.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa is in charge of writing an article for the school newspaper, so in hopes of encourage her, Honoka takes her, Shiho, and Rina to a woman named Mitoya, who runs an odango shop. She announces her plans to close it, but after seeing their article starts to reconsider.

33.TitleEnglish: Stock up your courage! Nagisa's troublesome birthday!!
33.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa's birthday has come up and the girls decide to spend the day observing flowers. However, Nagisa is more focused on her attempt to confess her feelings to Fujimura after she gets to spend time with him.

34.TitleEnglish: Friends on a journey! Zakennah on a field trip!?
34.SummaryEnglish: It's the first day of the field trip and Nagisa and Honoka takes a look at some of the features in Kyoto. Nagisa finds a lottery and wins two tickets, giving her and Honoka the chance to see an Edo drama. Meanwhile, Hikari feels worried after a series of weird event and Whisun comes out of the Chairect to tell her that "the truth is coming".

35.TitleEnglish: A seriously dangerous field trip! Lovely sliced fish has a dangerous smell
35.SummaryEnglish: Hikari joins the girls on their last day of the field trip. But strange events continue occurring as the little Boy from the Mansion observes Kyoto under the watchful eye of the inhabitants of the Mansion of Darkness.

36.TitleEnglish: Return to the pit! Polun and Lulun's great adventure
36.SummaryEnglish: Pollun and Lulun are are taken by a little girl after she mistakes them for stuffed animals someone threw away.

37.TitleEnglish: Nagisa's flying! Honoka's dancing! Feel the power of the harvest on the great stage!
37.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa attempts to make Shiho's newest play a big success but fears the worst as her friend continuously makes changes to it.

38.TitleEnglish: Goodbye, Honoka! Our bonds will intensify forever!
38.SummaryEnglish: Honoka is invited to move to Paris in order to be with her parents. But while she is excited by the prospect she is unsure if she is willing to leave everything else behind.

39.TitleEnglish: Burn out! The young Lacrosse finalist!!
39.SummaryEnglish: The Lacrosse Championship is beginning with Verone Academy going against Otagaku. In this time Nagisa bonds with Nagasawa, the captain of Otagaku's team and both girls reminisce about what encouraged them to play Lacrosse and how their feelings are about it now.

40.TitleEnglish: Together, we are the best! Full-powered rippin' roarin' Nagisa and Ryouta!
40.SummaryEnglish: After Ryouta is promoted to a higher badminton Club, Nagisa is tasked with taking him there. As the older sister she tries to show him support and is really excited, but this only causes him to try to avoid her.

41.TitleEnglish: Deliver your spirit! A wandering present of courage!
41.SummaryEnglish: With Fujimura's birthday approaching, Nagisa wants to get him a great gift. She is inspired to make something special but struggles to give it to him.

42.TitleEnglish: A rink full of sweethearts? Slipping and falling into grave danger!
42.SummaryEnglish: Nagisa is invited to the Amusement Park by Fujimura and it's a dream come true! But to her dismay, Honoka and Kimata were also invited. Together the four friends spend a day at the Amusement Park as Nagisa plans to work up the courage to confess her feelings for Fujipi.

43.TitleEnglish: The final winter vacation! It's a special lesson for Zakennah!
43.SummaryEnglish: With the school year almost over, a new captain is chosen for Science Club and Lacrosse. In this time everyone prepares to celebrate the holidays while trying to get to know the new captains.

44.TitleEnglish: The day Hikari disappears, the day we search for tomorrow!
44.SummaryEnglish: The balance between both worlds has began to shift, with those of the Mansion of Darkness, and those of the Garden of Light aware. Hikari then vanishes and runs into Hikaru, who questions the truth of his existence.

45.SummaryEnglish: After the disappearance of Hikari, the girls learn that she isn't remembered by anyone; although they know that something is missing. As the girls try to find her, the Evil King's resurrection isn't far off and the city is shown to be at risk.

46.TitleEnglish: Life-risking attack! Dark soldiers at maximum power!
46.SummaryEnglish: Shiny Luminous attempts to save Hikaru before the Evil King is resurrected. Meanwhile, Black and White continue to fight off the Generals.

47.TitleEnglish: Open the door! The story begins from here
47.SummaryEnglish: With the fate of the world on their shoulders, Pretty Cure is thrown into the Darkness and it is up to Luminous to save them and work together to defeat Baldez and the Evil King.
